title: Fix Soapui Shows Blank Screen When Opening on DWM
tags: @zettel _fix dwm soapui
roam-id: 95c8d1be-d5f6-41c6-a429-4e78ac0d25b8
type: text/markdown

put the following line in your `.zshrc` or `.bashrc`

``` shell
export _JAVA_AWT_WM_NONREPARENTING=1
```

source your `.zshrc` or open a new terminal then run `soapui` again
